<p><b>What is BRF+ in S4 Hana?</b> But doing output management via BRF+ is new in S/4 HANA from 1511 Version onwards. BRF+ is an application programming interface (API) and user interface for defining and processing business rule. It allows us to model rules in an intuitive way and to reuse these rules in different applications.</p>
